,{"type":"playsound","key":"$smallearthquake","volume":"0.6","id":77},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"2","xstrength":"4","ystrength":"4","vibrato":"20","randomness":"30","fadeout":"true","id":78},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_011#2","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":79},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":80},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"......","id":81,"figure":"avg_npc_011#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_011#2","name2":"avg_npc_053","focus":"2","id":82},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"萨卡兹战士","text":"混乱。这座城镇从来都不是上下一心的，就像蛋糕，切成一块一块。","id":83,"figure":"avg_npc_053"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"萨卡兹战士","text":"现在，那最后的一块也将要变成一盘散沙，他们毫无力量。","id":84,"figure":"avg_npc_053"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"萨卡兹战士","text":"就算我们收手，就算我们撤退，他们当真能活下来吗？","id":85,"figure":"avg_npc_053"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"萨卡兹战士","text":"莱塔尼亚必然会弃他们于不顾。","id":86,"figure":"avg_npc_053"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"萨卡兹战士","text":"离这里最近的两座移动城邦，二十四座高塔，没有一个大人物能俯瞰到冬灵山脉里垂死挣扎的小城镇。","id":87,"figure":"avg_npc_053"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_011#2","name2":"avg_npc_053","focus":"1","id":88},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"——悲哀。","id":89,"figure":"avg_npc_011#2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"我们曾是厌倦了这种悲哀，而站在这里，不要忘了。","id":90,"figure":"avg_npc_011#2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"不要试图自作主张。","id":91,"figure":"avg_npc_011#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_011#2","name2":"avg_npc_053","focus":"2","id":92},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"萨卡兹战士","text":"......当然。诶，你平时怎么不这么讲话呢？我只是抱怨抱怨。","id":93,"figure":"avg_npc_053"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"萨卡兹战士","text":"抱怨我们等待隐忍了那么久，最后的结果也没什么变化，事情还是变得很糟糕。","id":94,"figure":"avg_npc_053"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"萨卡兹战士","text":"只是一点不甘心的......牢骚。","id":95,"figure":"avg_npc_053"},{"type":"Dialog","id":96},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":97},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"1","xstrength":"8","ystrength":"6","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":98},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.7","r":"0.95",